</div>

<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Above_ground">Above ground</span></h2>
<p>You spawn in the top half of the 1st floor, and the bottom half of it contains:
</p>
<ul><li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Gasoline_pump" title="Gasoline pump">Gasoline pump</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Bike_helmet" title="Bike helmet">Bike helmet</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Cargo_pants" title="Cargo pants">Cargo pants</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Backpack" title="Backpack">Backpack</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Display_rack" title="Display rack">Display rack</a>
<ul><li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Uzi_9mm" title="Uzi 9mm">Uzi 9mm</a>
<ul><li>Uzi 9mm magazine</li>
<li>25 +P, 50 JHP</li></ul></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Machete" title="Machete">Machete</a></li></ul></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Bubblewrap" title="Bubblewrap">Bubblewrap</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Grenade" title="Grenade">Grenade</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Codeine" title="Codeine">10 portions of codeine</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Cigarettes" title="Cigarettes">A pack of 20 cigarettes</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Flashlight" title="Flashlight">Flashlight</a></li>
<li><a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Battery" title="Battery">Light disposable battery</a></li>
<li>A <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Plastic_bottle" title="Plastic bottle">plastic bottle</a> with 2 units of <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Water" title="Water">water</a></li></ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Below_ground">Below ground</span></h3>
<p>Below ground is identical in structure to the above ground, except with no loose items on the ground or in the display rack. There is also a 2x2 square of shallow water, if you get thirsty.
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Escaping">Escaping</span></h2>
<p>To escape, follow these three simple steps:
</p><p>1. Pour the gasoline from the gas pump onto the ground.
</p><p>2. Light the gasoline with a lighter or a grenade, although the grenade is less consistent.
</p><p>3. RUN AWAY!!!
</p><p>After some of the fire clears out, you can then adventure through the world as you please. However, there is a bug as of .6 in which you can't go down the stairs in any building but the tutorial room. Any attempt to do so is followed up with the prompt "There is something blocking the way about half-way down."
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="0.F">0.F</span></h3>
<p>As of 0.F, the lighter in the tutorial room no longer starts with butane inside of it. Here is an easy way to escape without lighter charge:
</p><p>1. Get to survival skill 2. This will automatically unlock the recipe for the fire drill item.
</p><p>2. Craft the fire drill item, and then stash everything else besides that into the underground floor, including breaking down the doors, smashing the display racks, and taking off the curtains on both floors, and bringing those resources down.
</p><p>3. Light 4 adjacent walls on fire with the fire drill. The easiest spot to do this is one of the corners.
</p><p>4. Get into the underground! Somehow, the fire above ground will not leak into the underground, unless you poured out fuel or something.
</p><p>5. Wait until you can't hear the crashing of a burning building anymore.
</p><p>6. Enjoy freedom!
</p><p>The underground bug still persists in 0.F, but besides that, you may now enjoy your world!
</p>
